      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Manna Dwehſele eekab-\nojahs/ un ilgojahs fohtt pehz ta\nUNGA Pagalmeem/ manna\nSirđô un mannas Meeſas pree-\najabs eekſch ta dſihwa STIP-\nRA DEEWA.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tas Putnis irr weenn\nNammu atraddie/ un ta Beſde-\niga tawn Ligſdu/ kur ta ſawus\nBehrnus iſperre/ pee taweem\naltaxeem KUNGS Zebâits/\nnans Rehniasch un mans\nDeews.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Swehtigi irr/ kas tawa\nNamna dſihwo/ tee flawe ten\nveenumebr/ Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Swehtigs irr tas Zilweks/\nas favn Stiprumu pee tewis\nneſle)/ kuzzu Sirđis (tawi)\netti stahw.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas zaur to Rauda-Fe-\ntju staiga/ un turr to paſchu\nar * awokſnainu Semmi/ ir\ne Mahzitaji tohp ar Swehti-\nhanahm tsgehrbtt.\n* Wiſneem irr tahds Preeks zaur Beh-\nahm Debbefu Walſtibá ee-eet, itt ka tee us\nukahm Plawahn ſtaigatu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee eet no weenas * Speh-\nbas us ohtru/ tee parahdifees\nreekſch Deewa eekſch Zianas.\n* Tas irr Uswarretchanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "KUNGS Deews Zebâits/\nanft mannu Luhgſchanu / at-\nrees tahs Ausis ak Jehkaba\nDeews! Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Deews muhfu * preekſch-\nirramas Bruxxas/ ſkattajs un\nstuhko tawa Swaidita Watgu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo weena Deena eekſch\ntaweemBagalmeem irr labbaka/\nne ka tuhkſtochas (zittas)/man\ngribbahs labbaki pee ta Decra\nNamna Sleegſna stahweht /\nne ka eekſch tahs Beedeeſwibas\nDſihwokteem mahioht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tas Deews KUNgs\nirr par Sauli un preekſchturra-\nmahm Brukkahm/ tas KUNgs\ndehs Scheblastibu un Gohdu/\nwisch to Labbumn ne atraus\nteem/ kas eekſch Menoseedsibas\nstaiga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "KUNGS Zebâits/ tweh-\ntigs irr tas Zilweks/ kas us tevi\npataujahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta LXXXV. Dseefina.\nWeena Luhgſchana/ ka Deews lihdsſchim scheß-\nligs bijis/ ta arridsan taggad un wehl jo-\nprohjam wiſch pahr ſaweem ſandim ap-\nschehlojees: 2/3/4. Un ka wiſch to ihſenu\nDeewa Kalpoſchanu uſturrecht: 9. Meeru/\nPeetizibu un Taigribu waldoht/ doht: 11/\n12. Un augligus Laikus schehligi doht\ngribbetu: 13.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eena Dseefina/ vreekſch\nfa augſta Dseedataja/\nſtarp teen Behrneem\nKorus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "KUNGS/ kas tu (zitt-\nkahrt) prett tawu Semmi leh-\nnigs bijis/ un Jehkaba Zeetumu\nnorwehrsis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas tu tawu Lauschu No-\nſeequmu eſti veedevis / un wiſ-\nfus wiſnu Grehkus apklahjis /\nSela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas tu wiſtu tawu Duf-\nZiiiii 2 mibu\n"
    }
  ],
